  {
    "client_msg_id": "8be3291a-9207-420c-8bba-f46bd84abc65",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "I guess I'm trying to avoid us falling into a local maximum wherein we can have end-users make buttons that send emails, post messages, or display spreadsheet calculations but don't give them the tools to do more complex and varied tasks. If you don't have higher bars in mind (regardless of where you choose to start), you could end up with another <https://coda.io> (which, while exciting and useful, is already something being developed by a competent team).",
    "user": "UCGAK10LS",
    "ts": "1565826526.057500",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_profile": {
